<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>OH, LET'S ALL ENDEAVOUR!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw I bawnun pang hitiu, lunggil leh theihtawp in,
 I Lalpau nasem in, A nasepa kipak in;
 Kipahman sa'n ma'n sep ding ahi tih hezing in,
 Pa deihbang leh A thu a semin, kipak hitiu.

[V2]
 Krista, Sapchuom di'n,
 Lalpa, bangcheng ka pie'u;
 Krista, Sapchuom di'n,
 Theihtawp in pang ung kau!

[V3]
 2. Aw I bawnun pang hitiu, Krista Lalgam ke'k di'n,
 Muntin hawla, gitloh apat thagau hukdam di'n
 Khawvel gam tina Chanchin Pha thu phuongzak dingin,
 Chitin, zat tinin Chanchin Pha a zak masieh un.

[V4]
 3. Aw I bawnun pang hitiu, Krista Sapchuom phut di'n,
 A nasep ah ginum in, I bangcheng Amah pie'n;
 A dan tincheng zawp a, a chawndan haw ngaisang in,
 Chun, Krista batna a khanglien in, hinkhuo beihma'n.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>269</hymn_number>
</song>